Recommendation 5
Recommendation:
 
The best way to prevent illness is to avoid being exposed to this virus. Health experts are begging US residents to:- 
1. Wear a mask to protect yourself and others and stop the spread of COVID-19.
2. Wash your hands often with soap and water for at least 20 seconds . Use hand sanitizer      especially after you have been in a public place
3. Avoid crowds until most people are vaccinated. The more people you are in contact          with, the more likely you are to be exposed to COVID-19.
